wiki.content:
"Applause" is a song by American recording artist Lady Gaga. It will be released as the lead single from her third upcoming studio album, ARTPOP. The song was written and produced by Lady Gaga and DJ White Shadow. Applause was premiered on mainstream radio stations in the United States on August 12, 2013.
